Class QRSwissBarcode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.swissqr.barcode.QRBarcode
      • ch.swissqr.barcode.QRCombinedBarcode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBarcode
    public class QRSwissBarcode
extends QRCombinedBarcode
implements IBarcode
    Generation of a Swiss QR Barcode Rest Webservice for the Generation of Swiss QR barcodes Barcode dimensions 46 x 46 mm Swiss cross logo measuring 7 x 7 mm. The maximum Swiss QR Code data content permitted is 997 characters (including the element separators). The version of the QR Code resulting with error correction level "M" and binary coding is version 25 with 117 x 117 modules.
    Author:
    pschatzmann
